===Etymology===
From {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*s-rik ~ *s-ryak||pheasant, partridge}} (STEDT; {{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}).
*Inside Chinese, cognate with {{och-l|翟|long-tailed pheasant}} and {{och-l|雒||a kind of bird}}.
*Outside Chinese, cognate with {{cog|my|ရစ်}}, {{cog|bo|སྲེག་པ|t=partridge}}, {{cog|lus|va-hrit}}. & possibly {{cog|cdm|tr=rut-waʔ}}.

